      <title>人工智能热潮涌入看涨的 Nvidia ETF，资金流入创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/inflows-into-bullish-nvidia-etf-hit-record-ai-frenzy-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年，随着人工智能的热潮，投资者纷纷涌入以英伟达为重点的交易所交易基金（ETF），资金流入一只追踪该芯片设计公司股价周三创下历史新高的看涨基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/inflows-into-bullish-nvidia-etf-hit-record-ai-frenzy-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 15:51:39 GMT</pubDate>
